{
  "texts": [
    "Practically, the model's Shannon Entropy not only gets bigger, but is gradually reduced with every new training that contains AI generated material.",
    "If we take into account the current pace of AI created content currently being published online, there is a definite sign that the next generation models will probably get worse and not better.",
    "In the end, perhaps it is more appropriate to talk about the possibility of a Natural Super Intelligence and not an artificial one.",
    "The example of technology itself, and its undeniable constant evolution, which is based on human cognitive abilities, seems to point in this direction.",
    "DiscussionArtificial intelligence is rapidly emerging as the most significant latest technological revolution of our era and offers the prospects for enormous progress."
  ]
}